                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8430" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2118</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1107 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">太保环责险：乘“科技”之势一路绝尘</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Taibao Environmental Liability Insurance: Taking Advantage of &quot;Science and Technology&quot; to Get Rid of the Dust all the Way</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑军，陈思</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国太平洋保险股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国太平洋保险；环境责任险；绿色金融；保险科技</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">China Pacific Insurance；Environmental Liability Insurance；Green Finance；Insurance Technolo</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022年2月28日，中国太保筹备了两年的太保科技有限公司终于落地。太保科技因背靠保险“三巨头”之一的中国太保公司，作为中国太保科技转型战略的产物，自成立那天起就广受关注。本案例以中国太平洋保险公司为例，主要介绍了中国太保顺应政策和时代背景主动出击，依托其强有力的科技基础背景，实行科技化转型战略，形成了“科技＋合作”的核心竞争优势，实现了环责险科技化从无到优的完美转变。旨在通过介绍太保产险的环责险科技转型实践，引导学员采用各种分析方法，剖析太保产险环责险发展科技转型的原因、采取的战略措施、具备的核心竞争力力及面临的挑战等。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On February 28, 2022, China Taibao Technology Co., Ltd., which had been preparing for two years, finally landed. As a product of China&#39;s Taibao technology transformation strategy, Taibao Technology has attracted a lot of attention since its establishment. This case takes China Pacific Insurance Company as an example. It mainly introduces China Pacific Insurance&#39;s policy and the background of the times. Relying on its strong scientific and technological foundation, it implements the scientific and technological transformation strategy, forms the core competitive advantage of &quot;science and technology + cooperation&quot;, and realizes the perfect transformation of environmental liability insurance from scratch to excellence. By introducing the environmental liability insurance technology transformation practice of Taibao Property Insurance, guide students to adopt various analysis methods to analyze the reasons for the scientific and technological transformation of the development of Taibao Property Insurance Environmental Liability Insurance, the strategic measures taken, the core competitiveness and the challenges faced.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">转型战略的分类；转型战略决定因素分析；风险识别与应对</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
